OL,3,CFirst Minister speaks to Prime
OL,4,CMinister over leaked devolution memo
OL,6,FThe First Minister of Wales has spoken
OL,7,Fto Sir Keir Starmer about his comments
OL,8,Fon devolution contained within a
OL,9,Fleaked memo.
OL,11,FIn the memo, which was sent in
OL,12,FDecember to senior Cabinet colleagues,
OL,13,Fthe Prime Minister tells them to
OL,14,Fresist opposition from devolved
OL,15,Fgovernments.
OL,17,FThe memo had been obtained by Plaid
OL,18,FCymru and earlier this week its leader
OL,19,FRhun ap Iorwerth accused the Prime
OL,20,FMinister of treating Wales with
OL,21,F"contempt".
OL,26,@}D@AOU}D@JO]
