FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773421881
OL,3,CFirst Minister speaks to Prime
OL,4,CMinister over leaked devolution memo
OL,6,FBaroness Eluned Morgan told members of
OL,7,Fthe Senedd's Committee for the
OL,8,FScrutiny of the First Minister that
OL,9,FSir Keir was referring to reserved
OL,10,Fareas of UK Government policy, such as
OL,11,Fhome affairs and defence, rather than
OL,12,Fdevolved matters like health and
OL,13,Feducation.
OL,15,F"I read the memo on Tuesday, and I was
OL,16,Fable to speak to the Prime Minister on
OL,17,FWednesday to get clarification on what
OL,18,Fhe meant within that letter," she told
OL,19,FMSs.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773421881
OL,3,CFirst Minister speaks to Prime
OL,4,CMinister over leaked devolution memo
OL,6,F"He made it clear to me that when he
OL,7,Fwas talking about direct delivery in
OL,8,Fthe nations, he was talking about
OL,9,Fissues reserved to the
OL,10,Fresponsibilities of the UK Government.
OL,12,F"That was something, and if you read
OL,13,Fthe letter carefully, it doesn't say
OL,14,Fin devolved areas.
OL,16,F"If you think about what the reserved
OL,17,Fareas are ` pensions, benefits, home
OL,18,Faffairs, immigration, foreign affairs
OL,19,F` those kind of areas."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773421882
OL,3,CFirst Minister speaks to Prime
OL,4,CMinister over leaked devolution memo
OL,6,F"The issue for us in the past is that
OL,7,Fpart of the problem is they have not
OL,8,Fdone enough in our country when the
OL,9,FTories were in charge," she said.
OL,11,F"We did not get the kind of money we
OL,12,Fshould have got for rail
OL,13,Finfrastructure.
OL,15,F"I'm really pleased now that we have
OL,16,Fbeen promised #14 billion of
OL,17,Fadditional funding. I want to see that
OL,18,Fmoney spent in Wales."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]sD@AOUwD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
