PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773421882
OL,3,CFirst Minister speaks to Prime
OL,4,CMinister over leaked devolution memo
OL,6,FThe First Minister was asked whether
OL,7,Fthe leaked memo showed that inter-
OL,8,Fgovernmental relations were currently
OL,9,F"strained".
OL,11,FMs Morgan replied: "I speak as I find.
OL,12,FI've been clear in terms of our
OL,13,Frelationships ministerially, that our
OL,14,Fministerial relationships are directly
OL,15,Fwith the UK Government departments.
OL,17,F"We don't go via the Wales Office and
OL,18,Fthat the relationships are
OL,19,Fconsiderably better than they have
OL,20,Fbeen under 14 years of Conservative
OL,21,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]sD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773421882
OL,3,CFirst Minister speaks to Prime
OL,4,CMinister over leaked devolution memo
OL,6,F"The fact that I can pick up the phone
OL,7,Fthe day after this comes out
OL,8,Fdemonstrates that we can have, and we
OL,9,Falways do have, robust conversations
OL,10,Fand clear conversations.
OL,12,F"But also, the fact that I can pick up
OL,13,Fthe phone demonstrates that actually
OL,14,Fthat relationship is in a very
OL,15,Fdifferent place from where it has been
OL,16,Ffor 14 years under the Conservatives."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
